Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, live-build (>= 3.0)
Recommends: live-boot-doc, live-config-doc, live-debconfig-doc, live-manual-all
Description: live-build configuration for the KDE live images
 live-image-kde-desktop contains the live-build configuration tree to build
 the KDE desktop live image.

