Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, live-build (>= 3.0)
Recommends: live-boot-doc, live-config-doc, live-debconfig-doc, live-manual-all
Description: live-build configuration for the LXDE desktop live images
 live-image-lxde-desktop contains the live-build configuration tree to build
 the LXDE desktop live image.

Package: live-image-rescue
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, live-build (>= 3.0)
Recommends: live-boot-doc, live-config-doc, live-debconfig-doc, live-manual-all
